WEBVTT

00:05.673 --> 00:08.467
<i>Hey, Dad, welcome to Railton.</i>

00:08.467 --> 00:11.137
<i>Just a couple questions.</i>

00:11.137 --> 00:13.431
<i>How come you didn't come to my wedding?</i>

00:13.431 --> 00:17.017
<i>Or want to meet your only grandchild?</i>

00:17.017 --> 00:20.855
<i>Or how could you abandon me</i>

00:20.855 --> 00:23.065
<i>when I had a rope around my neck?</i>

00:23.065 --> 00:25.985
<i>That's it, just those questions.</i>

00:25.985 --> 00:28.988
<i>Feel free to write
your answers on a postcard</i>

00:28.988 --> 00:31.323
<i>and mail it to me.</i>

00:32.450 --> 00:36.579
<i>Then we can go back
to avoiding each other.</i>

01:53.197 --> 01:54.448
I'm coming in!

01:54.448 --> 01:56.325
Dad! Get out!

02:03.415 --> 02:04.625
Hm...

02:11.757 --> 02:13.843
I almost took a shower with our daughter.

02:13.843 --> 02:15.469
She came in the night.

02:15.469 --> 02:16.887
She slept in her old room.

02:16.887 --> 02:18.180
What's that about?

02:18.180 --> 02:19.431
Mm...

02:19.431 --> 02:22.059
She didn't want to say,
she wanted to sleep.

02:22.059 --> 02:23.769
If we turned her room into a gym,

02:23.769 --> 02:25.020
this wouldn't happen.

02:25.020 --> 02:27.189
Or she'd get into great shape.

02:27.189 --> 02:29.316
- Bright side.
- Mm.

02:35.739 --> 02:37.950
- I saw my father on Tuesday.
- What?

02:39.910 --> 02:42.454
I was in my car.
I just wanted to get a glimpse.

02:42.454 --> 02:43.664
There he was.

02:46.292 --> 02:49.837
What did he say? Or just how... did it go?

02:49.837 --> 02:51.338
We didn't talk.

02:51.338 --> 02:53.173
I don't want to be lied to,

02:53.173 --> 02:58.053
and I only want to know
he's here because he's old,

02:58.053 --> 03:01.056
unemployed, and wants to be taken care of.

03:02.182 --> 03:04.685
- That's understandable.
- I'm going for a run.

03:04.685 --> 03:06.562
- Great.
- That's... important.

03:06.562 --> 03:07.980
Oh, it's my mom.

03:07.980 --> 03:09.607
Oh, yeah, she's been calling me.

03:09.607 --> 03:11.025
You too?

03:11.025 --> 03:14.028
- Did you talk to her?
- No, I wouldn't know what to say to her.

03:17.698 --> 03:19.825
Why haven't you answered my calls?

03:21.201 --> 03:24.121
Because my, um, caller ID works.

03:25.539 --> 03:28.125
You hurt your father very badly, you know.

03:28.125 --> 03:30.169
He played me the message you left.

03:30.169 --> 03:31.879
Oh, he's keeping my messages.

03:31.879 --> 03:33.339
What message?

03:33.339 --> 03:35.090
I left a message for my dad.

03:35.090 --> 03:37.301
I told him he's not welcome
here in Railton.

03:37.301 --> 03:40.596
It was a cruel thing to say.

03:40.596 --> 03:42.431
It stung him very badly.

03:42.431 --> 03:44.433
It was so over the line,

03:44.433 --> 03:45.976
Henry says he's leaving after the weekend.

03:45.976 --> 03:48.020
He says he's going to North Carolina.

03:48.020 --> 03:50.105
North Carolina? What's in North Carolina?

03:50.105 --> 03:51.440
Oh,

03:51.440 --> 03:53.817
a graduate student
that he hasn't seduced yet.

03:53.817 --> 03:57.571
- Gruen.
- What's that, the monster from <i>Beowulf?</i>

03:57.571 --> 03:59.073
His second wife.

04:00.532 --> 04:03.744
It would be a terrible situation for him,

04:03.744 --> 04:06.914
living out the last of his days

04:06.914 --> 04:09.249
in a place he has no connection to,

04:09.249 --> 04:12.336
far from any family...

04:12.336 --> 04:14.129
And the monster's Grendel.

04:14.129 --> 04:15.714
Well, you tell him
to have a nice trip,

04:15.714 --> 04:18.926
and the monster is Grendel's mom.

04:18.926 --> 04:20.302
Hank!

04:20.302 --> 04:23.389
This is something
that's very important to me.

04:23.889 --> 04:25.474
He'll leave for good

04:25.474 --> 04:28.143
if you don't come by and ask him to stay.

04:29.812 --> 04:31.480
I'm not going to do that.

04:32.564 --> 04:34.858
I'm asking you.

04:36.235 --> 04:37.945
Hank isn't available this weekend.

04:37.945 --> 04:40.906
He has a conference.

04:41.073 --> 04:42.950
Is that true?

04:42.950 --> 04:45.202
It's true I've been invited
to a conference,

04:45.202 --> 04:46.662
in Harrisburg.

04:46.662 --> 04:49.039
Oh, you can skip that.

04:49.665 --> 04:51.583
You have a choice to make

04:51.583 --> 04:53.961
between your father

04:53.961 --> 04:57.256
and an insignificant regional conference.

06:17.377 --> 06:18.754
It's good for guys to have a thing.

06:18.754 --> 06:20.297
This conference is kind of our thing.

06:22.007 --> 06:23.801
And the one year you decided to pull out

06:23.801 --> 06:25.135
is the one year I'm presenting.

06:25.135 --> 06:26.553
I was beginning to take it personally.

06:26.553 --> 06:29.348
Yeah, I've had
a lot going on, you know.

06:29.348 --> 06:30.933
Oh, sure, sure, sure.

06:30.933 --> 06:33.310
It's just that you decided
not to come weeks ago,

06:33.310 --> 06:34.853
like the minute you saw the program

06:34.853 --> 06:36.980
with my name and photo
prominently displayed on it.

06:36.980 --> 06:38.941
- I did?
- Mm-hm.

06:38.941 --> 06:41.777
I think we have a different definition
of "prominent".

06:41.777 --> 06:43.362
It's page three. Page three is the best.

06:43.362 --> 06:44.738
Phew...

06:44.738 --> 06:47.116
I got two other pages
that will knock your socks off.

06:48.408 --> 06:49.743
Let's go.

06:51.662 --> 06:53.664
I hope I don't meet anyone from last year.

06:53.664 --> 06:55.207
- You probably won't.
- Or the year before.

06:55.207 --> 06:59.211
Uh, Rosencrantz
and <i>Senor</i> Guildenstern, please.

06:59.211 --> 07:00.629
How many times have you heard that today?

07:00.629 --> 07:02.339
Beats the Nietzsche brothers.

07:02.339 --> 07:03.674
No, it does not.

07:03.674 --> 07:05.843
Devereaux and Conigula.

07:06.552 --> 07:08.137
Go right to page three?

07:08.846 --> 07:10.639
Whoa, whoa.

07:10.639 --> 07:12.808
I did not know Gracie
was going to be here.

07:12.808 --> 07:14.935
Quick, hand me my fake mustache.

07:14.935 --> 07:16.270
You've got a beard.

07:16.436 --> 07:19.940
Right. So, my Austin Powers teeth.

07:19.940 --> 07:22.234
You're too kind.
Look at her, holding court.

07:22.234 --> 07:24.278
Wait till they find out she's an idiot.

07:24.278 --> 07:26.363
