08:30.510 --> 08:32.596
and landed in a lady's drink, right?

08:32.596 --> 08:34.264
Uh, that was you.

08:34.264 --> 08:36.308
I prefer to be remembered for my work...

08:36.308 --> 08:37.392
- Well...
- ...but I'll take it.

08:37.392 --> 08:39.811
Hank's a novelist,
so it's his job to be kind of a dick.

08:39.811 --> 08:41.104
Ah.

08:41.104 --> 08:42.189
